SELECT u.user_id, count(a.activity_id) as activity_count FROM user_activity a JOIN dashboard_data d ON a.user_id = d.user_id JOIN user_activity u ON a.user_id = u.user_id GROUP BY u.user_id HAVING activity_count > 5 ORDER BY activity_count DESC;
